```

Auto-sort routing rules (in `OneDrive-Sort.ps1`):
- PDF/DOCX with "cv|resume|curriculum" → `Recruiting\Candidates\_Inbox\`
- PDF/DOCX with "jd|job description|requisition" → `Recruiting\Job Descriptions\_Inbox\`
- Video (.mp4 / .mov / .mkv / .m4v / .webm / .avi) → `Content\_Inbox\`
- Installer (.zip / .exe / .msi / .dmg / .iso / .7z / .rar) → `_Archive\Installers\`
- Dev debris (.py / .pyc / .pyi / .h / .lib / no-ext) → `_Archive\Downloads-DevDebris\`
- Everything else → `_Inbox\Downloads-Triage\`
- Triage files older than 30 days → `_Archive\Downloads-Old\`

### File Routing Rules

1. Pick up raw files from `/inbox/`
2. Process using the relevant skill from `/skills/`
3. Drop finished work in `/review/` for Bryan's approval
4. Once Bryan approves, file to the correct permanent location
5. Log what happened in `/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`

Never delete files — archive to `/archive/` instead.

### Archive Triggers

Move to `/archive/` when: company acquired or shut down, requisition formally closed, candidate placed or withdrawn, 12 months with no activity, account classified as Dead.

